title: Metal Men Various
description:
Collection of most of the Metal Men special appearances through the years, including Brave and the Bold as well as a number of Superman related comics. There are even a couple of Justice League Europe thrown in. Covers everything from the 1960s to today.

Be warned, some of the issues are in the cumbersome jpeg format.

Thanks to the scanners and uploaders. I pulled more than a few of these off some very large, though nearly dead, torrents that people had gone out of their way to create and keep alive.

Enjoy.
